 najčešće je to,

673
00:26:30,420 --> 00:26:31,760
 Bog mi zabranjuje nešta,

674
00:26:31,760 --> 00:26:33,540
 ako ja predam svoj život Bogu,

675
00:26:33,540 --> 00:26:34,600
 ako ja krenem u crkvu,

676
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:36,480
 Bog će mi nešta uskratiti,

677
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:37,480
 i,

678
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,560
 onda mi uvijek, ono,

679
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:40,300
 odgovorimo na to pitanje,

680
00:26:40,300 --> 00:26:40,460
 ono,

681
00:26:40,460 --> 00:26:41,680
 ko je prva laž u Bibliji,

682
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:43,000
 ono,

683
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:44,980
 kad su Adam i Eva bili u Edenskom vrtu,

684
00:26:44,980 --> 00:26:45,880
 i,

685
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:46,680
 Bog im kaže,

686
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:48,000
 jedite sa svih stabala,

687
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:49,440
 sa sveg jedite,

688
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:51,160
 ali s jednog stabla nemojte jesti,

689
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:52,860
 i,

690
00:26:52,860 --> 00:26:54,080
 oni,

691
00:26:54,080 --> 00:26:55,440
 Bog ode,

692
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:57,440
 i Adam i Eva pojedu sa stabla,

693
00:26:57,440 --> 00:26:58,520
 i, ono,

694
00:26:58,520 --> 00:26:59,860
 Bog sad želi pričat s njima,

695
00:26:59,860 --> 00:27:00,140
 ono,

696
00:27:00,140 --> 00:27:00,480
 želi,

697
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:01,760
 želi vidjeti šta se dogodilo,

698
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:02,740
 i,

699
00:27:02,740 --> 00:27:03,980
 Adam onda prebacuje,

700
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:04,380
 govori,

701
00:27:04,380 --> 00:27:04,980
 žena me,

702
00:27:05,580 --> 00:27:06,220
 zavela,

703
00:27:06,220 --> 00:27:08,360
 šta je Bog zapravo rekao,

704
00:27:08,360 --> 00:27:09,080
 ono,

705
00:27:09,080 --> 00:27:10,500
 jedite sa svih stabala,

706
00:27:10,500 --> 00:27:11,880
 ono,

707
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:13,340
 Džavo je već u knjizi postanka,

708
00:27:13,340 --> 00:27:15,600
 tu nagrdio sliku Boga,

709
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:15,880
 ono,

710
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,400
 zara vam,

711
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:18,060
 zara vam je Bog rekao da,

712
00:27:18,060 --> 00:27:19,640
 da ne jedete sa svih stabala,

713
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:20,480
 šta je Bog rekao,

714
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,480
 jer jedite sa svih,

715
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:22,560
 s jednog nemoj,

716
00:27:22,560 --> 00:27:23,460
 i, ono,

717
00:27:23,460 --> 00:27:24,540
 i dan danas je tako,

718
00:27:24,540 --> 00:27:24,740
 ono,

719
00:27:24,740 --> 00:27:26,080
 ako premam život Bogu,

720
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:27,640
 ne mogu imat suru,

721
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,080
 ne smijem igrati nogomet,

722
00:27:29,080 --> 00:27:30,640
 ne smijem imat novaca,

723
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:32,200
 ne smijem voziti dobar auto,

724
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,760
 morat ću ići svaki dan na misu,

725
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:33,980
 da,

726
00:27:33,980 --> 00:27:35,800
 morat ću molit 15 kronica dnevno,

727
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:37,000
 ići na 10 misa,

728
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,240
 ne znam nijakak živjeti,

729
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:38,440
 ono,

730
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:38,900
 to opće,

731
00:27:38,900 --> 00:27:40,340
 to opće nije istina.

732
00:27:40,340 --> 00:27:40,780
 E,

733
00:27:40,780 --> 00:27:41,440
 a kaj bi rekli,

734
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,100
 ok,

735
00:27:42,100 --> 00:27:42,640
 znači,

736
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:43,800
 oba dvoje ste rekli slično,

737
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:45,800
 ima i u krivu sliku,

738
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:47,960
 mladi,

739
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:49,200
 sami od sebe,

740
00:27:49,200 --> 00:27:49,940
 htio sam reći mi,

741
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:51,440
 ja više nisam tu toliko,

742
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:51,680
 ali,

743
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,020
 dakle,

744
00:27:52,020 --> 00:27:54,260
 ti sam od sebe,

745
00:27:54,260 --> 00:27:54,740
 mislim,

746
00:27:54,740 --> 00:27:55,660
 ne možeš imat sliku,

747
00:27:55,980 --> 00:27:57,920
 sliku imaš kakvu pokupiš kroz život.

748
00:27:57,920 --> 00:28:00,460
 Čija je prva odgovornost

749
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:02,120
 za stvorit tu sliku?

750
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:03,600
 Jel to obitelj,

751
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:04,560
 pretpostavljan da je?

752
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:06,680
 Jel to odgovornost i,

753
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:07,660
 ne znam,

754
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:08,220
 župnika,

755
00:28:08,220 --> 00:28:09,340
 s tim da recimo župnik

756
00:28:09,340 --> 00:28:10,580
 ne može puno,

757
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:12,760
 ukoliko ne dolaze u crkvu?

758
00:28:12,760 --> 00:28:14,880
 Jel to vjeronauk,

759
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:16,980
 osnovnoškolski,

760
00:28:16,980 --> 00:28:17,860
 srednjoškolski?

761
00:28:17,860 --> 00:28:19,360
 Jesi to prijatelji?

762
00:28:19,560 --> 00:28:20,480
 Znači,

763
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:22,000
 jel to da,

764
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:22,920
 ne znam,

765
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:25,280
 crkva kao šira crkva,

766
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:25,880
 znači mi,

767
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,380
 da premalo idemo van,

768
00:28:27,380 --> 00:28:31,280
 na platforme u kojima se mladi kreću,

769
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:34,400
 čija je to odgovornost da imaju krivu sliku?

770
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:36,260
 Ako se uopće,

771
00:28:36,260 --> 00:28:36,480
 evo,

772
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:37,540
 pitaću Don Tomu,

773
00:28:37,540 --> 00:28:39,860
 ako se uopće Tomu slažeš da

774
00:28:39,860 --> 00:28:42,720
 to nije samo njihova odgovornost,

775
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,180
 je,

776
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:43,940
 ok,

777
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:45,860
 on bira ako što kaže šta će pojest,

778
00:28:45,860 --> 00:28:47,940
 ali on pokupi,

779
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:50,320
 možda ono,

780
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:51,980
 ono komu se najbolje produo

781
00:28:51,980 --> 00:28:53,200
 i komu se najviše nametnuo?

782
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,880
 Jel mi tu svi negdje malo,

783
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,440
 malo ovoga puštamo?

784
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:57,340
 Da, pa,

785
00:28:57,340 --> 00:28:58,260
 mislim,

786
00:28:58,260 --> 00:28:59,220
 mi stariji,

787
00:28:59,220 --> 00:29:00,480
 mi stariji,

788
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:01,940
 ovaj,

789
00:29:01,940 --> 00:29:04,020
 znamo,

790
00:29:04,020 --> 00:29:06,420
 znamo za sve krivit mlade,

791
00:29:06,420 --> 00:29:07,140
 djecu,

792
00:29:07,140 --> 00:29:07,480
 a,

793
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:09,480
 od te generacije nema ništa od njih,

794
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:10,780
 mi kad smo bili mladi,

795
00:29:10,780 --> 00:29:11,400
 ovako onako,

796
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:13,140
 koliko puta čujemo te priče,

797
00:29:13,140 --> 00:29:13,360
 ono,

798
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:14,700
 dombosko na aparatima,

799
00:29:14,700 --> 00:29:15,680
 okreće se u grobu,

800
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:17,300
 u smislu,

801
00:29:17,300 --> 00:29:18,300
 ono,

802
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:20,420
 mi smo krivi,

803
00:29:20,420 --> 00:29:21,800
 mi smo krivi,

804
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:22,940
 zato što,

805
00:29:22,940 --> 00:29:23,260
 ono,

806
00:29:23,260 --> 00:29:24,120
 zato što,

807
00:29:24,120 --> 00:29:27,300
 nismo brinuli za te mlade

808
00:29:27,300 --> 00:29:28,140
 i zato što,

809
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:28,380
 ono,

810
00:29:28,380 --> 00:29:31,120
 puštamo da te mlade odgaja neko drugi,

811
00:29:31,120 --> 00:29:33,660
 jer mi nismo možda dovoljno prisutni s njima,

812
00:29:33,660 --> 00:29:35,140
 ne razgovaramo o temama

813
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:37,080
 koje njih zanimaju,

814
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:38,160
 koje oni prolaze,

815
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:40,600
 ne učimo ih nekom kritičkom stavu

816
00:29:40,600 --> 00:29:41,480
 i tim stvarima,

817
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:41,740
 ono,

818
00:29:41,740 --> 00:29:42,600
 mladi,

819
00:29:42,600 --> 00:29:43,220
 ono,

820
00:29:43,220 --> 00:29:44,060
 dobro,

821
00:29:44,060 --> 00:29:45,360
 ima donekle krivice

822
00:29:45,360 --> 00:29:46,060
 i kod njih,

823
00:29:46,060 --> 00:29:46,380
 ono,

824
00:29:46,380 --> 00:29:47,660
 poslije sedam godina

825
00:29:47,660 --> 00:29:49,180
 imaju svoj razum razvijen,

826
00:29:49,180 --> 00:29:49,920
 ali,

827
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:52,540
 većinom je kod nas krivica

828
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:54,200
 i onda ovo što se reka,

829
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:54,940
 ko proda,

830
00:29:54,940 --> 00:29:56,080
 bolje priču,

831
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:56,400
 taj,

832
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:56,800
 ono,

833
00:29:56,800 --> 00:29:58,140
 taj prođe

834
00:29:58,140 --> 00:29:59,360
 i,

835
00:29:59,360 --> 00:30:01,180
 nažalost,

836
00:30:01,180 --> 00:30:03,140
 mi stariji smo ponekad,

837
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:03,920
 ono,

838
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:06,220
 u zaostatku velikom.

839
00:30:06,220 --> 00:30:08,980
 Prije je bila razlika između kulture,

840
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:11,060
 između mog tate i mene,

841
00:30:11,060 --> 00:30:11,580
 ono,

842
00:30:11,580 --> 00:30:11,920
 dobro,

843
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:12,980
 30 godina,

844
00:30:12,980 --> 00:30:13,940
 tu je razlika,

845
00:30:13,940 --> 00:30:15,560
 vam reći,

846
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:17,020
 a sad je razlika,

847
00:30:17,020 --> 00:30:19,620
 u pet godina se svijet mijenja drastično.

848
00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:20,220
 I,

849
00:30:20,220 --> 00:30:21,240
 šta se dogodilo,

850
00:30:21,240 --> 00:30:24,120
 neki rastijep između generacija,

851
00:30:24,120 --> 00:30:26,740
 roditelji više ne mogu pratiti,

852
00:30:26,740 --> 00:30:28,080
 što se događa s djecom.

853
00:30:28,140 --> 00:30:32,180
 o nekim temama,

854
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:32,840
 ono,

855
00:30:32,840 --> 00:30:33,420
 koje su,

856
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:36,400
 koje su možda donekle i tabu teme i te stvari,

857
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:36,980
 jednostavno,

858
00:30:36,980 --> 00:30:37,180
 ono,

859
00:30:37,180 --> 00:30:37,920
 ne mogu,

860
00:30:37,920 --> 00:30:38,960
 ne mogu upratiti

861
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:42,560
 i ne znaju niti kako odgovoriti na neke stvari.

862
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:43,800
 Dok, ono,

863
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,840
 svijet se razvija i mladi, ono,

864
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:49,640
 mladi postaju odgajani od strane društvenih mreža,

865
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:51,520
 od strane influencera,

866
00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:52,900
 od strane nekih, ono,

867
00:30:52,900 --> 00:30:54,420
 ljudi koji, ono,

868
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:55,700
 ne žele njihovo dobro,

869
00:30:55,700 --> 00:30:57,080
 nego žele profit i da se,

870
00:30:57,080 --> 00:30:59,000
 da se okreće ekonomija u svijetu,

871
00:30:59,000 --> 00:30:59,500
 je o to je.

872
00:30:59,500 --> 00:31:01,000
 I tako da, ono,

873
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:03,180
 mi stariji smo krivi,

874
00:31:03,180 --> 00:31:05,060
 to sigurno,

875
00:31:05,060 --> 00:31:08,700
 ne bi ni na sad da smo pre krivi u smislu,

876
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:09,040
 ono,

877
00:31:09,040 --> 00:31:11,780
 nismo ni mi krivi što se svijet toliko brzo razvijao

878
00:31:11,780 --> 00:31:14,180
 i što ne znamo odgovoriti na neke stvari,

879
00:31:14,780 --> 00:31:15,600
 ali, ono,

880
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:16,780
 trebamo,

881
00:31:16,780 --> 00:31:17,580
 mislim,

882
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:18,640
 ako nekog voliš,

883
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:21,240
 onda težiš upoznat što više,

884
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:22,640
 što on prolazi i to sve.

885
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:24,940
 Ako volimo našu djecu i mladi,

886
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:26,480
 onda ćemo se pokušati, ono,

887
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:28,320
 staviti u njihovu situaciju,

888
00:31:28,320 --> 00:31:29,620
 probati vidjeti šta prolaze,

889
00:31:29,620 --> 00:31:30,880
 probati razgovarati s njima,

890
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:31,660
 gledati sine,

891
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:32,200
 kćeri,

892
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:32,820
 ono,

893
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:33,500
 kritički,

894
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:34,380
 ovaj,

895
00:31:34,380 --> 00:31:36,060
 pokušati razgovarati o stvarima,

896
00:31:36,180 --> 00:31:38,140
 tako da prvi odgajatelji,

897
00:31:38,140 --> 00:31:38,540
 naravno,

898
00:31:38,540 --> 00:31:39,520
 ostaju roditelji,

899
00:31:39,520 --> 00:31:42,040
 bez obzira na taj razcijep između generacijat,

900
00:31:42,040 --> 00:31:43,280
 ona ne može biti izlika,

901
00:31:43,280 --> 00:31:46,000
 a onda i mi kao crkva u smislu

902
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:46,820
 hjerarhija,

903
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:49,460
 odnosno župnici i svećenici,

904
00:31:49,460 --> 00:31:50,340
 časne sestre,

905
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:51,280
 isto trebamo,

906
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:52,600
 mislim,

907
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:55,600
 trebamo reći sebi dobro,

908
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:58,900
 prije je mlade odgajala jedna ulica,

909
00:31:58,900 --> 00:31:59,800
 sedih odgaja,

910
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:00,560
 druga ulica,

911
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:01,320
 to je, na primjer,

912
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:04,240
 digitalna ulica i sve ti mediji

913
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:05,260
 koji utječu na njih.

914
00:32:05,260 --> 00:32:06,480
 trebamo reći dobro,

915
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:07,800
 prije je sve moglo reći,

916
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:10,440
 poslušaj šta svećenik kaže

917
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,300
 i to ti je istina,

918
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:12,340
 danas nije tako,

919
00:32:12,340 --> 00:32:15,200
 trebamo upotrebiti neke nove alate,

920
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,700
 bolje im objasniti stvari,

921
00:32:16,700 --> 00:32:18,460
 motivirati ih i tako dalje,

922
00:32:18,460 --> 00:32:20,960
 to mislim da je tu i na nama,

923
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:21,640
 svećenicima,

924
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:22,600
 časnim sestrama,

925
00:32:22,600 --> 00:32:24,380
 odgovornost

926
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:27,760
 i najmoćnija stvar po meni,

927
00:32:27,760 --> 00:32:29,780
 ovo što je Timon isto govorio,

928
00:32:29,780 --> 00:32:34,700
 nužno je upoznat tu djecu i mlade

929
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:36,560
 sa nekim starijim mladima

930
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:37,780
 koji idu u crku,

931
00:32:37,780 --> 00:32:39,400
 koji su osjetili dragoga Boga

932
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:41,580
 i koji radosno žive svoju vjeru.

933
00:32:41,580 --> 00:32:42,340
 Ko uzore.

934
00:32:42,340 --> 00:32:43,600
 Tako je, ko uzore,

935
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:44,760
 jer ono,

936
00:32:44,760 --> 00:32:45,120
 ono,

937
00:32:45,120 --> 00:32:45,740
 to je to,

938
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:48,200
 ti adolescenska dob,

939
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,180
 to je dob uzora.

940
00:32:49,180 --> 00:32:50,700
 I tu onda,

941
00:32:50,700 --> 00:32:52,180
 to je najjača stvar,

