00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:17,680
 i,

1215
00:38:17,680 --> 00:38:18,460
 i stvarno,

1216
00:38:18,460 --> 00:38:18,760
 ono,

1217
00:38:18,760 --> 00:38:21,420
 baš ovo što je Don Tomo rekao,

1218
00:38:21,420 --> 00:38:22,000
 ono,

1219
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:25,640
 čovjek danas koji priča mladima,

1220
00:38:25,640 --> 00:38:27,320
 mora biti svjedok.

1221
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:30,120
 Mora biti svjedok i jednostavno,

1222
00:38:30,120 --> 00:38:30,420
 ono,

1223
00:38:30,420 --> 00:38:31,680
 moramo, ono,

1224
00:38:31,680 --> 00:38:33,240
 moramo svjedočiti mladima,

1225
00:38:33,240 --> 00:38:33,940
 ono,

1226
00:38:33,940 --> 00:38:37,580
 osobne iskustva i što kaže na kraju katekizam katoličke crkve,

1227
00:38:37,580 --> 00:38:40,860
 sakramentalizaciji mora prethoditi evangelizacija.

1228
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:42,020
 Ono,

1229
00:38:42,020 --> 00:38:43,900
 mi moramo jednostavno, ono,

1230
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:44,900
 dovesti te mlade,

1231
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:47,020
 da oni upoznaju,

1232
00:38:47,020 --> 00:38:50,120
 da oni dožive taj susret sa gospodinom,

1233
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:52,540
 a onda ih polako ulačiti,

1234
00:38:52,540 --> 00:38:52,840
 ono,

1235
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:53,620
 u sakramente,

1236
00:38:53,620 --> 00:38:54,840
 objašnjati ih sakramente.

1237
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,860
 Ja sjećam kak je meni ono bilo na,

1238
00:38:56,860 --> 00:39:00,380
 kad sam išao ko klinac na misu,

1239
00:39:00,380 --> 00:39:00,580
 ono,

1240
00:39:00,580 --> 00:39:02,040
 dođeš tamo i ono brojiš,

1241
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:02,700
 ovako, ono,

1242
00:39:02,700 --> 00:39:03,680
 gore lampice,

1243
00:39:03,680 --> 00:39:05,020
 brojiš pločice po podu,

1244
00:39:05,020 --> 00:39:05,720
 niš ne znaš.

1245
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:07,480
 Onda kad ti je došao,

1246
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,780
 ko što sam i rekao,

1247
00:39:08,780 --> 00:39:09,200
 Matija,

1248
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:10,900
 ili neki mlađi lik,

1249
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:12,100
 koji to stvarno živi,

1250
00:39:12,100 --> 00:39:13,360
 koji ima uvjerenje u to,

1251
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:14,220
 kojeg, ono,

1252
00:39:14,220 --> 00:39:15,280
 ne možeš poljuljati

1253
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,480
 i koji to doživio,

1254
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:18,420
 kad ti ono objasni šta je,

1255
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:19,520
 šta se tu događa,

1256
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:21,800
 na kraju kad ti to doživiš,

1257
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:22,300
 ono,

1258
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:24,440
 to te tjera da ti dođeš na misu,

1259
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,740
 da budeš prisutan,

1260
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:26,000
 ono,

1261
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:28,000
 to te tjera da imaš osobnu molitvu.

1262
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,320
 Tako da, ono,

1263
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,800
 ja mislim da je to prevažna stvar,

1264
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,140
 suradnja svećenika i...

1265
00:39:32,140 --> 00:39:33,560
 Da, jedan od razloga

1266
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:34,780
 za kje smo išli u ovu temu

1267
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:36,060
 i držimo se novima,

1268
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:38,520
 malo stari i mladima,

1269
00:39:38,520 --> 00:39:39,560
 znači, govorimo nekakva

1270
00:39:39,560 --> 00:39:40,180
 srednja škola,

1271
00:39:40,180 --> 00:39:41,280
 početak faksa je to,

1272
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:44,040
 je zato kje smo skužili

1273
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:46,820
 da mlađa djeca,

1274
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:47,920
 baš djeca,

1275
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:48,960
 ono, vrtić,

1276
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,260
 početak osnovne škole,

1277
00:39:50,260 --> 00:39:53,300
 tu je više stvar odgoja

1278
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:54,740
 i njih roditelji imaju

1279
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:55,860
 nekak pod kontrolom.

1280
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:57,500
 Znači, tu djecu možeš,

1281
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:58,640
 ako je mama,

1282
00:39:58,640 --> 00:40:00,600
 ima mogućnost biti doma,

1283
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:03,200
 pa ih ona oblikuje,

1284
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:04,540
 možeš ih upisati u,

1285
00:40:04,540 --> 00:40:06,560
 ne znam, katolički vrtić,

1286
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,560
 možeš ih upisati u katoličku osnovnu,

1287
00:40:08,560 --> 00:40:09,520
 okej, ima je srednjih,

1288
00:40:09,520 --> 00:40:12,140
 ali tu ih još nekak ti sam

1289
00:40:12,140 --> 00:40:13,260
 možeš uokvirit.

1290
00:40:13,260 --> 00:40:16,860
 Kasnije, adolescenti,

1291
00:40:16,860 --> 00:40:20,500
 više ih nemaš toliko pod kontrolom.

1292
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:22,100
 Dođe krizma,

1293
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:23,700
 obično se zna ono,

1294
00:40:23,700 --> 00:40:24,780
 sarkastična reč,

1295
00:40:24,780 --> 00:40:26,540
 vidimo se na, ne znam,

1296
00:40:26,540 --> 00:40:27,880
 vinčanju ili tako nešto.

1297
00:40:29,980 --> 00:40:31,340
 meni je zanima,

1298
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:37,220
 kak te koji se odvoje,

1299
00:40:37,220 --> 00:40:38,580
 nas koji smo se odvojili

1300
00:40:38,580 --> 00:40:39,320
 nakon krizme,

1301
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:40,500
 ja sam bio taj,

1302
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:42,960
 kaj ih najviše privuće?

1303
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:44,400
 Da li postoje,

1304
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,260
 recimo, crkva organiziruje jako puno

1305
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:46,960
 kampova,

1306
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:47,720
 ljetnih kampova,

1307
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:49,980
 postoji oratori koji je otvoren

1308
00:40:49,980 --> 00:40:51,880
 pet, šest, sedam dana na runu.

1309
00:40:52,820 --> 00:40:56,120
 Kaj ih najlakše privuće?

1310
00:40:56,120 --> 00:40:56,900
 Jesu to kampovi,

1311
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:57,620
 jesu to oratori?

1312
00:40:57,620 --> 00:41:00,120
 Je li to možda običan susret sa mladima,

1313
00:41:00,120 --> 00:41:02,360
 pa on ima nekakvu teškoću,

1314
00:41:02,360 --> 00:41:05,180
 pa mu se ti pokažeš kao neko ko bez interesa mu želi pomoći?

1315
00:41:05,180 --> 00:41:06,480
 Znači, kaj ste vidjeli svom razu

1316
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:08,320
 da najlakše privuće mlade

1317
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,120
 nakon što su,

1318
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:09,920
 na primjer,

1319
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:10,860
 nakon krizme otišli?

1320
00:41:13,260 --> 00:41:20,340
 Ako svećenik ću pričati,

1321
00:41:20,340 --> 00:41:21,960
 sigurno sve te ispovjede,

1322
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:23,740
 ono, iskustvo sve te ispovjedi,

1323
00:41:23,740 --> 00:41:24,860
 ne znam,

1324
00:41:24,860 --> 00:41:27,420
 ili trebaju biti kumovi,

1325
00:41:27,420 --> 00:41:29,240
 ili, ne znam,

1326
00:41:29,240 --> 00:41:31,140
 nešto ih,

1327
00:41:31,140 --> 00:41:32,860
 da, nešto ih,

1328
00:41:32,860 --> 00:41:33,920
 ono, znaju ljudi,

1329
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:36,720
 nisam mogao više, nešto me potaknulo

1330
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:37,600
 da dođem to,

1331
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:38,900
 i ona dođu na ispovjedi,

1332
00:41:38,900 --> 00:41:40,900
 ono, dožive na ispovjedi baš neko, ono,

1333
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:42,800
 povratak neki,

1334
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,340
 ono, ja s tim ljudima,

1335
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:46,600
 to je s tim mladima koji se nisu pojedili dugo,

1336
00:41:46,600 --> 00:41:48,460
 ono, kažem, prvo dobrodošao u kući,

1337
00:41:48,460 --> 00:41:49,500
 a onda sve ostalo.

1338
00:41:49,500 --> 00:41:53,140
 To je sigurno možda najmoćnija stvar,

1339
00:41:53,140 --> 00:41:54,440
 jer ono, tu baš osjete,

1340
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:56,400
 ono, Boga koji im, ono, oprašta,

1341
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:58,160
 bez obzira što su se udaljeli,

1342
00:41:58,160 --> 00:42:00,520
 i koji je sretniji od njih,

1343
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:02,280
 što su se vratili, nek što su oni, evo.

1344
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:05,500
 To sigurno, onda druga stvar,

1345
00:42:05,500 --> 00:42:09,480
 ti, naravno, ti kampovi, oratori,

1346
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:12,400
 koji nisu privlačni samo,

1347
00:42:12,740 --> 00:42:14,900
 onima koji su ostali u crkvi,

1348
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:17,100
 nego i onima koji nisu toliko u crkvi.

1349
00:42:17,160 --> 00:42:18,600
 Je li dolaze mladi van crkve?

1350
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:21,400
 Pitam zato kaj,

1351
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:24,540
 ja sam išao na jedan ljetni kamp,

1352
00:42:24,540 --> 00:42:26,140
 kod Don Damirana Postorje,

1353
00:42:26,140 --> 00:42:27,520
 ali sjećam se da je moja prva reakcija

1354
00:42:27,520 --> 00:42:29,980
 tih prvih par puta kad su me zvali,

1355
00:42:29,980 --> 00:42:31,400
 bilo, pa dobro,

1356
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:32,680
 ljetovanje s crkvom,

1357
00:42:32,680 --> 00:42:34,680
 stvarno, sa svećenikom,

1358
00:42:34,680 --> 00:42:36,300
 pa kao nije to za ili sirotinju,

1359
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:39,660
 ili ono, za ljude koji stvarno nemaju

1360
00:42:39,660 --> 00:42:40,800
 s nikim otići na more,

1361
00:42:40,940 --> 00:42:42,500
 pa onda ajde svi u grupi,

1362
00:42:42,500 --> 00:42:44,340
 vas 40 koji nema prijatelja,

1363
00:42:44,340 --> 00:42:45,380
 pa ćete se međusobno družiti.

1364
00:42:45,380 --> 00:42:46,780
 Ili stvarno,

1365
00:42:46,780 --> 00:42:48,860
 dolaze mladi van crkve,

1366
00:42:48,860 --> 00:42:51,260
 ili mislim koji nisu već unutra

1367
00:42:51,260 --> 00:42:53,160
 u oratoriju ili u zajednici?

1368
00:42:53,780 --> 00:42:56,500
 Pa dolaze, mislim dolaze kampovi,

1369
00:42:56,500 --> 00:42:58,120
 to koliko god je sa crkvom

1370
00:42:58,120 --> 00:42:59,020
 i sa svećenikom,

1371
00:42:59,020 --> 00:43:00,560
 pe na neki način privlačno je,

1372
00:43:00,560 --> 00:43:02,460
 još bude niža cijena,

1373
00:43:02,460 --> 00:43:04,900
 ono danas za ljetovat pod navodnike,

1374
00:43:04,900 --> 00:43:07,100
 ti ono previsoke su cijena,

1375
00:43:07,100 --> 00:43:09,340
 ono ti imaš kamp sad na prviću

1376
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:11,520
 ili na postiri za tako nisku cijenu,

1377
00:43:11,520 --> 00:43:12,680
 pa idem, šta me briga,

1378
00:43:12,680 --> 00:43:14,180
 ne trebam ja previše ulaziti

1379
00:43:14,180 --> 00:43:15,760
 u to što oni rade.

1380
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:17,140
 Ubitno mogu s jednom daje.

1381
00:43:17,140 --> 00:43:19,060
 Pa da, i to, i nekad bude to,

1382
00:43:19,060 --> 00:43:20,880
 neki okidači ono dođu

1383
00:43:20,880 --> 00:43:23,340
 i onda, ono, se promijene na tom kampu

1384
00:43:23,340 --> 00:43:25,900
 i oratori sam po sebi,

1385
00:43:25,900 --> 00:43:27,460
 ono, Dombosko je rekao,

1386
00:43:27,460 --> 00:43:29,900
 ono, volite ono što vole mladi

1387
00:43:29,900 --> 00:43:32,140
 da bi mladi zavoli ono što vi volite,

1388
00:43:32,140 --> 00:43:34,560
 to jest, ono, u smislu,

1389
00:43:34,560 --> 00:43:36,620
 stolni tenis, stolni nogomet,

1390
00:43:36,620 --> 00:43:37,740
 nogomet glazba,

1391
00:43:37,740 --> 00:43:39,660
 ambijent za druženje,

1392
00:43:39,660 --> 00:43:41,800
 pokraj crkve mi imamo tamo oratori,

1393
00:43:41,800 --> 00:43:43,220
 svaku večer je otvoren

1394
00:43:43,220 --> 00:43:46,600
 i dođu mladi koji nisu toliko u vjeri

1395
00:43:46,600 --> 00:43:48,180
 i onda malo pomalo s njima

1396
00:43:48,180 --> 00:43:50,740
 dođeš do tih stvari koje ti voliš,

1397
00:43:50,820 --> 00:43:51,560
 odnosno vjera,

1398
00:43:51,560 --> 00:43:53,280
 odnosno vrijednosti neke

1399
00:43:53,280 --> 00:43:55,480
 sveta misa, sveta ispovjedi i to.

1400
00:43:55,480 --> 00:43:56,840
 Tako da, ono,

1401
00:43:56,840 --> 00:43:58,960
 ovaj, to, mislim da je,

1402
00:43:58,960 --> 00:44:00,960
 mislim da je prebitan taj način

1403
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:02,580
 u kojem, ono, se pod navodnike

1404
00:44:02,580 --> 00:44:04,500
 spustiš na neku njihovu razinu

1405
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:05,440
 da bi ih pridobio

1406
00:44:05,440 --> 00:44:06,680
 i kad oni tebe onda vide

1407
00:44:06,680 --> 00:44:07,460
 da si s njima

1408
00:44:07,460 --> 00:44:09,580
 u tim nekim stvarima

1409
00:44:09,580 --> 00:44:10,320
 koje oni vole,

1410
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:12,120
 onda će te čak i poštivati,

1411
00:44:12,120 --> 00:44:13,500
 poštivati ću onu tvoju riječ,

1412
00:44:13,500 --> 00:44:14,680
 onaj tvoj poticaj,

1413
00:44:14,680 --> 00:44:15,340
 na ispovjed,

1414
00:44:15,340 --> 00:44:16,600
 na sve tu misu i tako.

1415
00:44:16,660 --> 00:44:17,280
 tako da, evo,

1416
00:44:17,280 --> 00:44:20,060
 kampove oratori sigurno, ono,

1417
00:44:20,060 --> 00:44:21,500
 su, su jako, jako

1418
00:44:21,500 --> 00:44:22,640
 dobro sredstvo za to.

1419
00:44:22,640 --> 00:44:23,860
 Timone, kak ti,

1420
00:44:23,860 --> 00:44:25,500
 ti znam da puno tog vodiš

1421
00:44:25,500 --> 00:44:26,720
 od kampova do projekata,

1422
00:44:26,720 --> 00:44:27,600
 pa...

1423
00:44:27,600 --> 00:44:30,080
 Pa, to je i moje iskustvo, ono,

1424
00:44:30,080 --> 00:44:31,000
 ja sjećam kad,

1425
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:32,280
 nakon te krizme,

1426
00:44:32,280 --> 00:44:34,400
 ono, baš su bile, ono,

1427
00:44:34,400 --> 00:44:34,920
 prijelomice,

1428
00:44:34,920 --> 00:44:36,360
 da li ostati u zajednici,

1429
00:44:36,360 --> 00:44:38,260
 upravo ono što smo na početku

1430
00:44:38,260 --> 00:44:39,100
 pričali, ono,

1431
00:44:39,100 --> 00:44:40,340
 možda ću morati ići

1432
00:44:40,340 --> 00:44:41,300
 na pet misla dnevno,

1433
00:44:41,300 --> 00:44:42,280
 možda ću morati, ono,

1434
00:44:42,280 --> 00:44:43,820
 moliti petna iz krunica,

1435
00:44:43,820 --> 00:44:45,640
 i baš tad, ono,

1436
00:44:45,640 --> 00:44:46,860
 nekako se to posložilo,

1437
00:44:46,860 --> 00:44:48,760
 da to ljeto,

1438
00:44:48,760 --> 00:44:49,960
 nisam uspio dogovoriti,

1439
00:44:49,960 --> 00:44:51,140
 ono, nikakvo ljetovanje,

1440
00:44:51,140 --> 00:44:52,480
 ono, nisam htio više

1441
00:44:52,480 --> 00:44:53,580
 ići sa svojima,

1442
00:44:54,200 --> 00:44:55,300
 ono, malo ti sramić,

1443
00:44:55,300 --> 00:44:57,220
 ono, srednja škola, ono,

1444
00:44:57,220 --> 00:44:58,560
 bilo me sram, ono,

1445
00:44:58,560 --> 00:44:59,920
 iću sad s mamom na more,

1446
00:44:59,920 --> 00:45:00,760
 iću s mamom,

1447
00:45:00,760 --> 00:45:01,840
 i zapravo, ono,

1448
00:45:01,840 --> 00:45:03,160
 to su stvari koje muče

1449
00:45:03,160 --> 00:45:04,040
 današnje, ono,

1450
00:45:04,040 --> 00:45:05,040
 tinejdžere, ono.

1451
00:45:05,040 --> 00:45:07,200
 Da, na nama može biti smiješno,

1452
00:45:07,200 --> 00:45:08,260
 ali u stvari njima je to briga.

1453
00:45:08,260 --> 00:45:09,060
 Da, ono,

1454
00:45:09,060 --> 00:45:10,220
 ono se želi odvojiti

1455
00:45:10,220 --> 00:45:11,060
 od svojih roditelja,

1456
00:45:11,060 --> 00:45:11,640
 želi, ono,

1457
00:45:11,640 --> 00:45:13,540
 kad se odvojiti od roditelja,

1458
00:45:13,540 --> 00:45:14,980
