00:51:17,820 --> 00:51:19,700
 Da li ja,

1717
00:51:19,700 --> 00:51:24,480
 kao dobar roditelj koji pokušavam bit,

1718
00:51:24,480 --> 00:51:25,860
 njemu trebam reći,

1719
00:51:25,860 --> 00:51:27,900
 znači ne zanimaš me uopće,

1720
00:51:27,900 --> 00:51:30,440
 u osam i svaku večer krunica imaš molit s nama,

1721
00:51:30,520 --> 00:51:32,340
 ne zanima me koliko ti sad daje ili ne da.

1722
00:51:32,340 --> 00:51:33,860
 Ide se minimalno,

1723
00:51:33,860 --> 00:51:35,460
 ne da idem na misu.

1724
00:51:35,460 --> 00:51:36,180
 Ne zanima me,

1725
00:51:36,180 --> 00:51:37,760
 niš me ne zanima,

1726
00:51:37,760 --> 00:51:38,360
 to se mora.

1727
00:51:38,360 --> 00:51:40,920
 Ali tako riskiram,

1728
00:51:40,920 --> 00:51:43,520
 da mu stvorim pressing

1729
00:51:43,520 --> 00:51:46,000
 i da on jedva čeka da otiđe od doma

1730
00:51:46,000 --> 00:51:47,720
 i da skine i mene

1731
00:51:47,720 --> 00:51:49,760
 i mamu sa vrata.

1732
00:51:49,760 --> 00:51:51,140
 Ili, s druge strane,

1733
00:51:51,140 --> 00:51:51,500
 ok,

1734
00:51:51,500 --> 00:51:52,560
 kako hoćeš,

1735
00:51:52,560 --> 00:51:54,020
 ja ti dajem primjer,

1736
00:51:54,020 --> 00:51:55,580
 ja ti dajem mogućnost,

1737
00:51:56,140 --> 00:51:57,040
 ja ću molit za tebe.

1738
00:51:57,040 --> 00:51:59,060
 Evo, ja stvarno ne znam odgovoru.

1739
00:51:59,060 --> 00:52:01,100
 Kaj je napraviti?

1740
00:52:01,100 --> 00:52:02,880
 Ako uopće ima odgovor?

1741
00:52:03,520 --> 00:52:07,460
 Moje iskustvo,

1742
00:52:07,460 --> 00:52:08,020
 iskustvo,

1743
00:52:08,020 --> 00:52:09,720
 kad gledam po zajednici,

1744
00:52:09,720 --> 00:52:10,980
 sad se jako puno

1745
00:52:10,980 --> 00:52:13,240
 mladih i rodilo,

1746
00:52:13,240 --> 00:52:15,580
 zapravo djece se jako puno rodilo,

1747
00:52:15,580 --> 00:52:16,980
 a i ono jako puno mladih

1748
00:52:16,980 --> 00:52:20,520
 sve više ono i raste,

1749
00:52:20,520 --> 00:52:21,580
 zapravo članova,

1750
00:52:21,580 --> 00:52:22,820
 odnosno,

1751
00:52:22,820 --> 00:52:25,000
 članovi zajednice imaju djecu

1752
00:52:25,000 --> 00:52:27,900
 i ono sad baš ulaze

1753
00:52:27,900 --> 00:52:30,100
 u te tineđerske godine,

1754
00:52:30,100 --> 00:52:32,860
 nekako praksa je pokazala

1755
00:52:32,860 --> 00:52:34,060
 da obitelji koji skupa

1756
00:52:34,060 --> 00:52:34,900
 idu na misu,

1757
00:52:34,900 --> 00:52:37,260
 ono svaku nedelju,

1758
00:52:37,260 --> 00:52:39,120
 koje njeguju ono tu,

1759
00:52:39,120 --> 00:52:40,920
 to ozraći,

1760
00:52:40,920 --> 00:52:41,840
 ono molitveno,

1761
00:52:41,840 --> 00:52:45,240
 nekako kasnije ti mladi

1762
00:52:45,240 --> 00:52:46,040
 nemaju problema

1763
00:52:46,040 --> 00:52:47,160
 s odlaskom na misu.

1764
00:52:47,160 --> 00:52:50,380
 Imaju problema oni

1765
00:52:50,380 --> 00:52:52,380
 kojima crkva nije predstavljena,

1766
00:52:52,380 --> 00:52:53,460
 na primjer u mom slučaju,

1767
00:52:53,460 --> 00:52:54,340
 ono ja nisam ništ znao

1768
00:52:54,340 --> 00:52:54,680
 od crkvi,

1769
00:52:54,680 --> 00:52:56,100
 tako da me crkva nini zanimala,

1770
00:52:56,100 --> 00:52:58,440
 a šta dobiješ sa prisilom,

1771
00:52:58,440 --> 00:52:59,940
 šta dobiješ sa tom kontrolom,

1772
00:52:59,940 --> 00:53:00,820
 da ne znam,

1773
00:53:00,820 --> 00:53:01,620
 guraš nekog.

1774
00:53:01,620 --> 00:53:03,820
 Ja znam koliko mojih prijatelja,

1775
00:53:03,820 --> 00:53:05,460
 a i dan dana sviđam ono mlade,

1776
00:53:05,460 --> 00:53:07,560
 starcih ono guraju,

1777
00:53:07,560 --> 00:53:09,420
 ono moraš u crkvu nedelja,

1778
00:53:09,420 --> 00:53:11,840
 ono odi na misu,

1779
00:53:11,840 --> 00:53:13,960
 on ode u kvartovski kafić,

1780
00:53:13,960 --> 00:53:15,340
 provede tamo sat vremena,

1781
00:53:15,340 --> 00:53:16,800
 otvori si misna čitanja,

1782
00:53:16,800 --> 00:53:19,000
 u slučaju da ga mama i tata pita

1783
00:53:19,000 --> 00:53:20,400
 po kom je bilo evanđelje.

1784
00:53:20,400 --> 00:53:23,020
 I on zna po kom je bilo evanđelje,

1785
00:53:23,100 --> 00:53:23,940
 šta je svećini kreko,

1786
00:53:23,940 --> 00:53:26,080
 on kaže dvije, tri stvari

1787
00:53:26,080 --> 00:53:28,140
 i ono mama i tata misli da je on bio na misi.

1788
00:53:28,140 --> 00:53:29,800
 Sa tom kontrolom

1789
00:53:29,800 --> 00:53:35,020
 i prisilom misli da nećemo jako puno dobiti.

1790
00:53:35,020 --> 00:53:37,020
 Ja bi sigurno savjetovo rojiteljima

1791
00:53:37,020 --> 00:53:38,840
 da se posavjetuju s nekim

1792
00:53:38,840 --> 00:53:40,800
 ko radi s mladima.

1793
00:53:40,800 --> 00:53:43,720
 Jako puno rojiteljima čak i zna izvati

1794
00:53:43,720 --> 00:53:46,460
 ono kar vidi da su im djeca u problemu,

1795
00:53:46,460 --> 00:53:48,980
 nekom kar vidi da su počeli lagano ono

1796
00:53:48,980 --> 00:53:50,700
 odlaziti.

1797
00:53:50,700 --> 00:53:51,200
 Šta?

1798
00:53:51,200 --> 00:53:51,980
 Lelujat.

1799
00:53:51,980 --> 00:53:53,500
 Da, kad su počeli malo lelujat,

1800
00:53:53,500 --> 00:53:54,360
 onda me znaju zvati,

1801
00:53:54,360 --> 00:53:55,780
 ono ne znam šta da radim sa sinom.

1802
00:53:55,780 --> 00:53:58,440
 I ono, ja tu iskoristim priliku,

1803
00:53:58,440 --> 00:53:59,940
 malo se upoznam sa sinom,

1804
00:53:59,940 --> 00:54:00,900
 ono, izađemo van,

1805
00:54:00,900 --> 00:54:01,880
 popijemo piće,

1806
00:54:01,880 --> 00:54:03,920
 odemo na neki nogomet,

1807
00:54:03,920 --> 00:54:04,820
 odemo negdje,

1808
00:54:04,820 --> 00:54:07,780
 ono, podružimo se da upoznam to djete.

1809
00:54:07,880 --> 00:54:09,820
 I ono, najčešće, nažalosti,

1810
00:54:09,820 --> 00:54:11,640
 roditelji budu onak krivi,

1811
00:54:11,640 --> 00:54:12,780
 jer su ih stiskali.

1812
00:54:12,780 --> 00:54:14,220
 Moraš, moraš, moraš.

1813
00:54:14,220 --> 00:54:15,100
 Dakle, uđem.

1814
00:54:15,100 --> 00:54:17,240
 Don Tomo, tvoje iskustvo?

1815
00:54:17,240 --> 00:54:18,760
 Pa mislim,

1816
00:54:18,760 --> 00:54:22,280
 nijedan, ni drugi ekstrem nije dobar

1817
00:54:22,280 --> 00:54:22,900
 u smislu.

1818
00:54:22,900 --> 00:54:23,740
 Ako smo, ono,

1819
00:54:23,740 --> 00:54:25,340
 permisivni roditelji,

1820
00:54:25,340 --> 00:54:26,900
 pustimo, pa dobro,

1821
00:54:26,900 --> 00:54:28,740
 ako će ići, iće.

1822
00:54:28,740 --> 00:54:30,940
 I ono, on će sam odlučiti.

1823
00:54:30,940 --> 00:54:32,680
 Tako, ta stvar nije dobra.

1824
00:54:32,680 --> 00:54:34,740
 S druge strane, nije dobro prisiljavati

1825
00:54:34,740 --> 00:54:37,340
 i ono, moraš, moraš, moraš.

1826
00:54:37,520 --> 00:54:39,800
 Domboskovi je govorio

1827
00:54:39,800 --> 00:54:40,740
 tri stupa

1828
00:54:40,740 --> 00:54:43,020
 Domboskog odgojnog sustava

1829
00:54:43,020 --> 00:54:45,100
 su vjera, razum i ljubaznost.

1830
00:54:45,100 --> 00:54:47,220
 Znači, ne samo vjera,

1831
00:54:47,220 --> 00:54:48,300
 moraš u crkvu,

1832
00:54:48,300 --> 00:54:50,660
 nego razum zašto moraš u crkvu,

1833
00:54:50,660 --> 00:54:51,800
 to je zašto bi trebao

1834
00:54:51,800 --> 00:54:53,660
 i ljubaznost na ljubaza način

1835
00:54:53,660 --> 00:54:55,380
 to reći svome djetetu.

1836
00:54:55,380 --> 00:54:56,720
 Ono, dok sjedite,

1837
00:54:56,720 --> 00:54:57,900
 dok je raspoloženo,

1838
00:54:57,900 --> 00:54:59,360
 dok si, ne znam, i tako.

1839
00:54:59,360 --> 00:55:00,480
 Ovo dvoje bi još,

1840
00:55:00,480 --> 00:55:01,400
 da me pitaš,

1841
00:55:01,400 --> 00:55:02,440
 još bi nekak i zvuko.

1842
00:55:02,440 --> 00:55:03,480
 Ovo dvoje,

1843
00:55:03,480 --> 00:55:04,960
 ovog trećeg se ne bi sjetio, recimo.

1844
00:55:05,120 --> 00:55:06,120
 Da, da, da.

1845
00:55:06,120 --> 00:55:07,720
 I to, evo, prvo,

1846
00:55:07,720 --> 00:55:09,540
 tako, nijedan, nijedrugi ekstrem,

1847
00:55:09,540 --> 00:55:11,080
 a druga stvar, ono,

1848
00:55:11,080 --> 00:55:12,880
 postepenost neka,

1849
00:55:12,880 --> 00:55:15,400
 znači, ono, malo prije smo govorili o tome,

1850
00:55:15,400 --> 00:55:16,620
 ono, ti se govorio,

1851
00:55:16,620 --> 00:55:18,740
 kako u nekoj ranijoj dobi,

1852
00:55:18,740 --> 00:55:19,840
 u djetinstvu,

1853
00:55:19,840 --> 00:55:20,400
 znači,

1854
00:55:20,400 --> 00:55:22,280
 djete ne zna što je dobro za njega.

1855
00:55:22,280 --> 00:55:24,620
 Djete ne zna da je misa dobra za njega.

1856
00:55:24,620 --> 00:55:26,560
 I tu ja doslovno trebam,

1857
00:55:26,560 --> 00:55:27,220
 djete, ono,

1858
00:55:27,220 --> 00:55:28,160
 svojim primjerom,

1859
00:55:28,160 --> 00:55:28,620
 idemo,

1860
00:55:28,620 --> 00:55:29,240
 nedjelja je,

1861
00:55:29,240 --> 00:55:30,180
 ide se na misu.

1862
00:55:30,180 --> 00:55:31,440
 Drago djete,

1863
00:55:31,440 --> 00:55:32,120
 znači,

1864
00:55:32,120 --> 00:55:33,520
 mami i tati,

1865
00:55:33,520 --> 00:55:35,540
 je misa bitnija od ručka.

1866
00:55:35,540 --> 00:55:36,860
 Ono,

1867
00:55:36,860 --> 00:55:37,480
 u smislu,

1868
00:55:37,480 --> 00:55:39,980
 viš kako mi nedjeljni ručak bude svećan,

1869
00:55:39,980 --> 00:55:41,900
 misa je nešto još bitnije,

1870
00:55:41,900 --> 00:55:43,080
 oblačimo se tako,

1871
00:55:43,080 --> 00:55:43,800
 tako i tako.

1872
00:55:44,120 --> 00:55:44,320
 Znači,

1873
00:55:44,320 --> 00:55:46,280
 od malena usađiva djetetu to,

1874
00:55:46,280 --> 00:55:46,900
 dok još,

1875
00:55:46,900 --> 00:55:47,180
 ono,

1876
00:55:47,180 --> 00:55:49,380
 djete još ne razumije da je to dobro za njega

1877
00:55:49,380 --> 00:55:50,640
 i naravno da ćeš tu ga,

1878
00:55:50,640 --> 00:55:51,440
 ono,

1879
00:55:51,440 --> 00:55:51,920
 ono,

1880
00:55:51,920 --> 00:55:53,180
 u smisu šta mi radimo,

1881
00:55:53,180 --> 00:55:54,280
 to ćeš i ti raditi.

1882
00:55:54,280 --> 00:55:55,960
 Ako nisi išao na misu,

1883
00:55:55,960 --> 00:55:56,540
 ono,

1884
00:55:56,540 --> 00:55:57,100
 u jednom trenutku,

1885
00:55:57,100 --> 00:55:58,300
 ako nisi išao na misu,

1886
00:55:58,300 --> 00:55:58,980
 dobro,

1887
00:55:58,980 --> 00:56:01,300
 to je jedna zajednička stvar koju mi radimo,

1888
00:56:01,300 --> 00:56:04,320
 onda nema ni na izlet koji je zajednička stvar,

1889
00:56:04,320 --> 00:56:06,340
 ili, neću reći, nema ručka,

1890
00:56:06,340 --> 00:56:07,380
 ali, ono,

1891
00:56:07,380 --> 00:56:07,900
 u smisu,

1892
00:56:07,900 --> 00:56:08,860
 na taj način,

1893
00:56:14,120 --> 00:56:15,680
 ne zato što smo policajci,

1894
00:56:15,680 --> 00:56:17,160
 no zato što želimo dobro djetetu,

1895
00:56:17,160 --> 00:56:18,440
 znamo da je dobro za njega.

1896
00:56:18,440 --> 00:56:20,400
 Naravno da ćeš mu dati tu stvar

1897
00:56:20,400 --> 00:56:21,580
 ako znaš da je dobro za njega.

1898
00:56:21,580 --> 00:56:23,740
 U dobiju adolescencije

1899
00:56:23,740 --> 00:56:26,800
 događa se to da djeca postaju samostalno,

1900
00:56:26,800 --> 00:56:29,020
 žele se odvajati od roditelja,

1901
00:56:29,020 --> 00:56:30,960
 što je dobra stvar i potrebna stvar

1902
00:56:30,960 --> 00:56:32,180
 i Bogu hvala da je tako

1903
00:56:32,180 --> 00:56:34,220
 i neku svoju autonomiju i to sve.

1904
00:56:34,220 --> 00:56:36,720
 E tu počinje i do dobra zuma,

1905
00:56:36,720 --> 00:56:38,900
 gdje ove tri stvari onda treba spojiti,

1906
00:56:38,900 --> 00:56:40,420
 ono, gdje trebaš,

1907
00:56:40,420 --> 00:56:40,960
 ono,

1908
00:56:40,960 --> 00:56:42,080
 djetetu,

1909
00:56:42,080 --> 00:56:42,660
 ono,

1910
00:56:42,800 --> 00:56:45,260
 ponovno objasniti možda na vjeronauku u školi

1911
00:56:45,260 --> 00:56:47,140
 ili kod župnika koji je starije kova,

1912
00:56:47,140 --> 00:56:49,640
 nije shvatilo bogatstvo sve te mise

1913
00:56:49,640 --> 00:56:51,640
 i onda pomoću nekih priča,

1914
00:56:51,640 --> 00:56:53,240
 usporedbi ili nečega,

1915
00:56:53,240 --> 00:56:53,860
 ono,

1916
00:56:53,860 --> 00:56:54,900
 objasniti djetetu,

1917
00:56:54,900 --> 00:56:56,520
 ono koje sedmi, osmi raze,

1918
00:56:56,520 --> 00:56:57,020
 zašto?

1919
00:56:57,020 --> 00:56:58,760
 I naravno svojim primjerom,

1920
00:56:58,760 --> 00:56:59,000
 ono,

1921
00:56:59,000 --> 00:57:01,220
 kad djeta vidi da se mama ode ispovjediti

1922
00:57:01,220 --> 00:57:01,940
 prije njega

1923
00:57:01,940 --> 00:57:03,440
 ili tata prije njega,

1924
00:57:03,440 --> 00:57:04,320
 još više tata,

1925
00:57:04,320 --> 00:57:04,560
 ono,

1926
00:57:04,560 --> 00:57:05,900
 muškarce kad vide da moli,

1927
00:57:05,900 --> 00:57:07,280
 to je to još utjecajnije,

1928
00:57:07,660 --> 00:57:08,580
 onda će i djete,

1929
00:57:08,580 --> 00:57:10,320
 znači dob primjera,

1930
00:57:10,320 --> 00:57:11,740
 mame i tate,

1931
00:57:11,740 --> 00:57:13,320
 dob razuma,

1932
00:57:13,320 --> 00:57:14,520
 objasniti zašto,

1933
00:57:14,520 --> 00:57:15,600
 koriste neku sliku,

1934
00:57:15,600 --> 00:57:16,060
 ja, ono,

1935
00:57:16,060 --> 00:57:16,380
 znam,

1936
00:57:16,380 --> 00:57:17,520
 uvijek toj dobi,

1937
00:57:17,520 --> 00:57:17,720
 ono,

1938
00:57:17,720 --> 00:57:19,460
 da dođe Kristijano ili Mesi,

1939
00:57:19,460 --> 00:57:19,900
 ono,

1940
00:57:19,900 --> 00:57:21,940
 vuka bi mamu i tatu za rukav,

1941
00:57:22,000 --> 00:57:23,320
 ajde vodi me na utakmicu,

1942
00:57:23,320 --> 00:57:24,840
 a čeće dolazi stvoritelj

1943
00:57:24,840 --> 00:57:26,200
 i Mesija i Kristijana,

1944
00:57:26,200 --> 00:57:26,760
 ono,

1945
00:57:26,760 --> 00:57:27,980
 stvoritelj cijelog svijeta,

1946
00:57:27,980 --> 00:57:28,240
 ono,

1947
00:57:28,240 --> 00:57:28,480
 tu,

1948
00:57:28,480 --> 00:57:29,060
 i ono,

1949
00:57:29,060 --> 00:57:29,960
 objasniti zašto,

1950
00:57:29,960 --> 00:57:30,200
 ono,

1951
00:57:30,200 --> 00:57:31,640
 zašto je bitna sve ta priča,

1952
00:57:31,640 --> 00:57:31,820
 isto,

1953
00:57:31,820 --> 00:57:32,040
 ono,

1954
00:57:32,040 --> 00:57:34,900
 primaš Isusa da bi postao slični njemu,

1955
00:57:34,900 --> 00:57:35,400
 o,

1956
00:57:35,400 --> 00:57:36,720
 evo,

1957
00:57:36,720 --> 00:57:37,820
 ali za to treba,

1958
00:57:37,820 --> 00:57:38,340
 naravno,

1959
00:57:38,340 --> 00:57:40,860
 provest vremena sa svojim djecom razgovarati,

1960
00:57:40,860 --> 00:57:42,340
 staviti to kao prioriteta,

1961
00:57:42,340 --> 00:57:43,960
 ne sto drugih aktivnosti

1962
00:57:43,960 --> 00:57:45,340
 koje nam danas svijet nameće,

1963
00:57:45,340 --> 00:57:46,420
 i tako dalje.

1964
00:57:46,420 --> 00:57:47,780
 Daj samo da te još pitam,

1965
00:57:47,780 --> 00:57:51,980
 spomenuo si kod Domboskovog odgojnog sustava,

1966
00:57:51,980 --> 00:57:55,320
 ja znam da je Dombosko spomenuo pristupnu točku,

1967
00:57:55,320 --> 00:57:56,900
 kaj je bila pristupna točka njegova?

